{"tid":1979045,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【龍門翻身】餿水奶茶獲平反 盧覓雪：畀78分！","createTime":"2020-04-19T06:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T11:39:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed5171b0a276f422e5bfaf9623d86c966b88b17","tid":1979045,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/food/20200419/4P5C5XJBCS52YPO2HCEAIVJQX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Ffood%2F20200419%2F4P5C5XJBCS52YPO2HCEAIVJQX4%2F&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWvolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=238fad7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Ffood%2F20200419%2F4P5C5XJBCS52YPO2HCEAIVJQX4%2F&h=a59eb9f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/food/20200419/4P5C5XJBCS52YPO2HCEAIVJQX4/</a><br />\n<br />\n【龍門翻身】餿水奶茶獲平反 盧覓雪：畀78分！<br />\n<br />\n兩星期後，我們再訪龍門，看看老闆張俊傑有沒有洗心革面，更請來盧覓雪齊齊踢館。「我嘅原則係入到餐廳食飯，好食就會話好食，唔好食就會話唔好食，理得你龍門幾黃啦！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【黃店風眼】餐飲界翹楚拯救「難食之首」龍門大翻身<br />\n<br />\n盧覓雪說。她亦有留意網民對龍門的劣評，「我都好驚訝，龍門係因為黃店起朵，我啲朋友仲叫我唔好去，話我會鬧爆佢！」張老闆聲稱，今日的龍門已痛改前非，隨即奉上之前試食的芝士吉列豬扒撈丁、咖喱吉列豬扒飯及熱奶茶，真的如我們的期望一樣，大成功！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200419/large/1587111149_9db9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200419%2Flarge%2F1587111149_9db9.jpg&h=5ca684fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩星期後，我們請盧覓雪到龍門冰室踢館。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200419/large/1587111148_29ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200419%2Flarge%2F1587111148_29ec.jpg&h=4e7c5500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龍門冰室出品的熱奶茶經常被網民揶揄味道如餿水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200419/large/1587111148_c273.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200419%2Flarge%2F1587111148_c273.jpg&h=062e3625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n芝士吉列豬扒撈丁，盧覓雪表示麵質爽口，芝士汁終於有芝士味。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多一倍芝士 「可接受的味道」<br />\n<br />\n「比我預期好好多！我最驚訝係撈丁嘅麵質，因為好多餐廳食到嘅即食麵或意粉，通常都好似一堆爛泥咁！佢呢個麵入口係相對爽口同分明！」芝士汁方面，盧表示：「茶餐廳嘅芝士撈丁裏面嘅芝士，其實全部都係我哋細細個用嚟夾面包、三文治嘅即食芝士，呢啲全部都唔係真芝士，不過佢呢隻人工芝士味，我接受！」張老闆表示，聽取「餐飲宗師」吳永皓的意見後，立即調整芝士在汁水裏的份量，「之前用9包卡夫芝士，而家就用夠18包，希望能夠帶出更濃的芝士味！」食物過關，被網民戲謔味如餿水的奶茶又如何呢？「我飲奶茶，首先要夠香！要先聞到佢；第二，入口要滑；第三就係茶味。龍門奶茶唯一缺點就係聞唔到佢嘅香味，但呢杯奶茶我覺得唔錯。整體嚟講，我會畀佢78分。（咁高？）你要記住，好多人都混淆咗，舉個例，去一間米芝蓮三星級餐廳食飯，我自然會用米芝蓮餐廳標準去點評，但我唔會用呢個要求去食茶餐廳。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄧偉傑、林京賢<br />\n攝影：黎家駒、羅捷豐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae74b298353076f57f80a0a840cf681a0a5c9505","tid":1979045,"uid":60206,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"我地食果d 咪照舊0分野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c7acf927a60b31ce9e1ee959c9ff2fa533b75b","tid":1979045,"uid":116194,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"最認同最尾個句，大佬茶記唔通想佢煮到曉飛咩"},{"pid":"bcc119f5b4ac44539544f58255dfef1977e3e746","tid":1979045,"uid":214036,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"290db142bc0c42c1ddc51c0ab286d1a88f1db8b9","tid":1979045,"uid":236075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae74b298353076f57f80a0a840cf681a0a5c9505","tid":1979045,"uid":60206,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"我地食果d 咪照舊0分野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla